VersionChecker - Class in com.github.sbugat.rundeckmonitor
Simple generic version checker on GitHub, inpect target jar and local jar build date to determinated if an update is available If one is found, download the full jar and replace the original jar via a double restart The checker use an independant thread to check and download the file.
